Wouldn't you know it, both of Leecifer's came back to us *undead*

name: Pink Holiday Garamon Greeting Card
description: A warm glow spreads across the quiet city, bringing the most special gift of all... Share the Kaiju Joy with your loved ones this year...Pink Holiday Garamon makes everything more festive. 5" x 7" high quality cardstock with glossy finish and envelope.

name: McGee's Alice in Wonderland 'Banksy' Custom Figure
description: 'Apologies to Banksy' Bomb Hugger vinyl figure completely resculpted from head to toe by Atom Gray, and re-emerging as gothic Alice from 'The Madness Returns' video game...clutching a white rabbit bunny bomb!

name: Custom Bandai Mefilas Sofubi Figure
description: A freaky kaiju monster from the world of Ultraman gets a bold updated look from Miss Magpie on this classic Japanese toy.

name: Deeptank GID Majin Bander Custom Sofubi
description:
Custom sculpted and painted kaiju by Atom Gray, from the 1960's 'Captain Ultra' Japanese TV series...

The tank assembly was added to enhance the underwater styling of this super cool monster, and the paint application leaves plenty of super-charged glow in the dark vinyl exposed.

Figure is also carefully weighted to allow display with the arms outstretched. Please note: due to the original factory molding in the neck area, the head will not turn without possibly damaging the paint. The arms and legs do articulate normally.

name: Custom TTToy Gulgo Sofubi
description: Sweet hand painted custom sharkboy vinyl toy by Miss Magpie, with a deep sea color palette and a dual matte/glossy finish.

name: Custom RealxHead Kintsukuroi Mutant Bigaro
description:
Inspired by the art of kintsukuroi (repairing precious objects like pottery with gold filling), Miss Magpie has customized this sofubi with lush tones and gold accents...

Bigaro's removable helmet has also been mounted on a spring to add height and lessen any possible paint wear against the body.

name: Schrödinger's Blind Box Resin Figure
description:
Based on Schrödinger's Cat, the infamous theoretical experiment by Erwin Schrödinger, and the Uncertainty Principle formulated by Werner Heisenberg...

In honor of our favorite quantum weirdness, we have created a limited first edition of 100 (50/50 alive/dead) resin cats.  Figure stands 3 1/4" tall.

Entirely handmade, and vaguely educational.

Please note: these are sold as sealed boxes only, i. e., ordering 2 does not guarantee receiving a pair of 1 each.

name: Play With Your Toys Sticker
description:
Highest quality full color 4" sticker, with our new PWYT design.

Free Domestic Shipping!

name: Cat Logo Diecut Sticker
description:
Top quality 4" die-cut sticker, featuring our Maneki Nekro Kitty.

Free Domestic Shipping!

name: Hello Cassy Magnet
description: Supercute recycled audio cassette in Hello Kitty style. Strong ceramic magnets on backside. Edition of 24. =^_^=

name: Island Classic Shrunken Head
description:
Edition of 25, cast in soft polyfoam with resin accessories. Hemp stitched, and featuring hand punched blended hair. Comes with display stand and hanging loop included. 

Approx. 8 in. standing.

name: Super7 Dokuwashi GID Custom Vinyl Toy
description: Wonderful hand painted Doku by Miss Magpie. Measures approx. 9" tall.

name: Secret Base Skullwing "Sun" Custom Vinyl Toy
description: Hand painted "Sun" Skullwing figure by Miss Magpie, measures approx. 4.5" tall. 3 point articulation.

name: Secret Base Skullwing "Moon" Custom Vinyl Toy
description: Hand painted "Moon" Skullwing figure by Miss Magpie, measures approx. 4.5" tall. 3 point articulation.

name: Hungry Little Devil Custom Vinyl Figure
description: Created by Atom Gray, this voracious dude is approx. 4.5" tall. Features soft flexible wings and an antique cocktail fork. 3 points of articulation. A perfect guest for your next dinner party...just keep a close eye on the deviled egg platter!

name: Custom Skull Zombi Vinyl Figure (Black)
description:
Handpainted custom version of the classic Vinyl Junkies toy by Atom Gray, with black teeth and claws. Features 3 point articulation and multi color doll eyes...great addition to any zombie or custom sofubi collection!

Approx. 5.25" tall.

name: Pink Holiday Garamon Tree
description:
Truly unique original sculpture, totally glitterific...

Garamon stands approx. 30" tall on a turntable base. Prewired with bright pink lights, includes the ultra-ornaments as well as the gift-wrapped city buildings.

Kaiju Delight that glows year round!
